ing: 2 honey graham crackers, crushed and divided
des: "Lemon yogurt, fresh blueberries, and honey graham crackers make an easy and delicious breakfast parfait. Tasty enough too for a light dessert. Eat immediately if you want crisp crunchy graham crackers."
ins: Spoon about half of the lemon yogurt into the bottom of a glass. Layer half the crushed graham crackers atop the yogurt. Pile about half the blueberries atop the graham cracker layer. Repeat layering.
